title: Verify a new healthcheck is added in the config file and listeners are updated for chain-proxy and explicit-proxy
custom_steps:
- Open /opt/ns/cfg/netskope.edge-proxy.cfg
- Check app-httpproxy-cloud-chain-clear-healthcheck added to app-httpproxy-healthcheck and new section for app-httpproxy-cloud-chain-clear-healthcheck is created
- Check listeners are updated for chain-proxy and explicit-proxy
custom_expected: Changes should be updated in the netskope.nsedgeproxy.cfg
